Add `query` or `TIB` class to a text input to enable the beautifier:

~~~ .html
<input type="text" class="query" value="foo, bar, baz">
~~~

Or use `query` type in the Panel API:

~~~ .php
return [
    'type' => 'query',
    'value' => 'foo, bar, baz'
];
~~~

*[API]: Application Programming Interface